    "summary": "In this transcript, a user asks a health-seeking question about the safety of taking 400mg of ibuprofen every two hours to manage severe back pain. The assistant repeatedly declines to provide definitive medical guidance, emphasizes the importance of following packaging instructions, and warns about the risks of exceeding maximum dosages and overdosing.",
